61
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:05,080
draws your eye to it because the action

62
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:07,640
is urgent. The avatar is there because

63
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:09,320
your eye can associate who did what way

64
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:10,960
faster than reading a name in the

65
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:12,959
column. And once you're thinking that

66
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:15,200
way, it's a pretty simple jump to adding

67
00:02:12,959 --> 00:02:17,280
a chart to roll up the data into a

68
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:19,120
summary. Because this data has a time

69
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:20,880
dimension, and our chart shows you that

70
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:22,480
