112
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:53,040
it, this is exactly what an onboarding

113
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:54,240
is. When a user lands on your app for

114
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:56,200
the first time, they shouldn't be

115
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:57,640
staring at a fully loaded dashboard

116
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:59,360
wondering where to start. A good

117
00:03:57,640 --> 00:04:01,200
