00:04:22,919 --> 00:04:26,280
disclosure, the spectrum of

131
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:28,680
explicitness, and the onboarding flows,

132
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:30,400
is to look at a lot of real software.

